892{
893 auto& vm = JSC::getVM(&lexicalGlobalObject);
894 auto throwScope = DECLARE_THROW_SCOPE(vm);
895 auto id = Identifier::fromString(vm, reinterpret_cast<const LChar*>("relList"), strlen("relList"));
896 auto valueToForwardTo = thisObject.get(&lexicalGlobalObject, id);
897 RETURN_IF_EXCEPTION(throwScope, false);
898 if (UNLIKELY(!valueToForwardTo.isObject())) {
899 throwTypeError(&lexicalGlobalObject, throwScope);
900 return false;
901 }
902 auto forwardId = Identifier::fromString(vm, reinterpret_cast<const LChar*>("value"), strlen("value"));
903 PutPropertySlot slot(valueToForwardTo, false);
904 asObject(valueToForwardTo)->methodTable(vm)->put(asObject(valueToForwardTo), &lexicalGlobalObject, forwardId, value, slot);
905 RETURN_IF_EXCEPTION(throwScope, false);
906 return true;
907}

1293
1294JSC::IsoSubspace* JSHTMLAnchorElement::subspaceForImpl(JSC::VM& vm)
1295{
1296 auto& clientData = *static_cast<JSVMClientData*>(vm.clientData);
1297 auto& spaces = clientData.subspaces();
1298 if (auto* space = spaces.m_subspaceForHTMLAnchorElement.get())
1299 return space;
1300 static_assert(std::is_base_of_v<JSC::JSDestructibleObject, JSHTMLAnchorElement> || !JSHTMLAnchorElement::needsDestruction);
1301 if constexpr (std::is_base_of_v<JSC::JSDestructibleObject, JSHTMLAnchorElement>)
1302 spaces.m_subspaceForHTMLAnchorElement = makeUnique<IsoSubspace> ISO_SUBSPACE_INIT(vm.heap, vm.destructibleObjectHeapCellType.get(), JSHTMLAnchorElement);
1303 else
1304 spaces.m_subspaceForHTMLAnchorElement = makeUnique<IsoSubspace> ISO_SUBSPACE_INIT(vm.heap, vm.cellHeapCellType.get(), JSHTMLAnchorElement);
1305 auto* space = spaces.m_subspaceForHTMLAnchorElement.get();
1306IGNORE_WARNINGS_BEGIN("unreachable-code")
1307IGNORE_WARNINGS_BEGIN("tautological-compare")
1308 void (*myVisitOutputConstraint)(JSC::JSCell*, JSC::SlotVisitor&) = JSHTMLAnchorElement::visitOutputConstraints;
1309 void (*jsCellVisitOutputConstraint)(JSC::JSCell*, JSC::SlotVisitor&) = JSC::JSCell::visitOutputConstraints;
1310 if (myVisitOutputConstraint != jsCellVisitOutputConstraint)
1311 clientData.outputConstraintSpaces().append(space);
1312IGNORE_WARNINGS_END
1313IGNORE_WARNINGS_END
1314 return space;
1315}
1316
1317void JSHTMLAnchorElement::analyzeHeap(JSCell* cell, HeapAnalyzer& analyzer)
1318{
1319 auto* thisObject = jsCast<JSHTMLAnchorElement*>(cell);
1320 analyzer.setWrappedObjectForCell(cell, &thisObject->wrapped());
1321 if (thisObject->scriptExecutionContext())
